{"tid":574631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有世界級雕塑　有幾多人識欣賞","createTime":"2018-02-27T14:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T15:53:17.000Z","uid":40525,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"46fcd5cc8ff6fc551c80b801b867be0eaaeb7f79","tid":574631,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/222200_c38feb5a4264177fc17c2dc3af845e86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F222200_c38feb5a4264177fc17c2dc3af845e86.jpg&h=d04a80e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n添馬公園突然出現一個大南瓜！黃色皮，黑色斑點，那是真的嗎？可以吃的嗎？當然不。這個南瓜是日本藝術家草間彌生的招牌雕塑《Pumpkin: big》，在日本四國地區直島也有類似的一個。但大南瓜為何突然到訪香港的維港海岸，成為港人拍照勝地？<br />\n<br />\n香港藝術中心主辦的「藝遊維港Habour Arts Sculpture Park」由今天起至4月11日，將於中西區海濱長廊、香港演藝學院、西區花園及香港藝術中心展出21件國際級雕塑，讓公眾免費欣賞。雕塑走出博物館，卻走進了大眾的生活，形成連場有趣的藝術互動。<br />\n<br />\n雖然大部分作品也出自國際級大師的手中，但亦不缺本地藝術家的蹤影。曾敏富的《Before Collapse》以腳掌雕塑反思人口不斷擴張的世界、黃國才的《Asteroids &amp; Comets》則以六件金色的鋼造雕塑象徵宇宙與生命的起源。黃榮法的《時・針（已逝某天的時間囊）》、何冠廷的《[[x]]》與王志勇的《舊燈塔的回憶》也以各自以擅長的材料，如大理石、鋼鐵及LED燈板，製作出別具特色的本地雕塑作品。<br />\n<br />\n「香港擁有一個優秀的藝術家群體。」Tim Marlow多次強調，本地藝術家的雕塑讓他留下深刻的印象，而整體的藝術氣氛亦在近年漸變成熟。本地藝術家製作了傑出的作品，大眾又會與藝術作出怎樣的互動，創造出怎樣的公共空間？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2FypqPE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FypqPE&d=ZavXTvnWBvWBpBSV81nf%2BS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a455e18f\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FypqPE</a>"},{"pid":"3a6b824dc47e26a9422888590cbb58e50ec1044f","tid":574631,"uid":9942,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"好多所謂世界級既藝術品都係吹棒出黎既姐<br />\n<br />\n真係唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"7e5d6b12c25d8289900c89a283a50fa836946805","tid":574631,"uid":116530,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:26:41.000Z","msg":"密集恐懼症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a024fa7cdffe30ba960d73a23169c8ebda0b6a","tid":574631,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"好撚核突<br />\n快d搬走啦屌"},{"pid":"36bf9375b5b8ea82cd49cdde899718981c513a3e","tid":574631,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a6b824dc47e26a9422888590cbb58e50ec1044f","tid":574631,"uid":9942,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"好多所謂世界級既藝術品都係吹棒出黎既姐<br />\n<br />\n真係唔識欣賞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:34:40.000Z","msg":"啲有錢人用黎洗黑錢"},{"pid":"a3bac08e6e3a40080a32764c85b271b829f9fe1d","tid":574631,"uid":123308,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130425/large/25la6p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130425%2Flarge%2F25la6p1.jpg&h=99d6f8c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fbe424b12c10679abd199c959ddab3e8b503bd6","tid":574631,"uid":33896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"草間？ 唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"78209040d14f05fabe75b388a0a9e028b1e65847","tid":574631,"uid":8858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"咩世界級先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"1c5747c2015fc3b43c048fa2f32a78e1d616a3f2","tid":574631,"uid":155344,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"世界級核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efea8d628e91ed81fdfc3fc9d4ced215ce808e9","tid":574631,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"google咗草間彌生 但個樣係黃一飛嚟㗎喎<br />\n草間彌生係咪即係黃一飛呢?"},{"pid":"f2d9dabfbd3b3cb9e44302b38549114f47652